modemu2k v0.2.3 - Hayes AT-command modem
emulator bridging a serial-style
interface to TCP/Telnet ("dials" out and
answers incoming connections) over IPv4
or IPv6. Ships as a C library
(libmodemu2k) plus a small CLI. Based on
modemu, by Toru Egashira (1995-1996).

github.com/theimpossibleastronaut/modemu2k
